asap.realizer.scheduler

Class BMLBBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • asap.realizer.scheduler.BMLBBlock

  • public class BMLBBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the state of a BML block used in ASAP. Captures the feedback of behaviors of a BML Block, and update the BML block state accordingly.
    Author:
    hvanwelbergen
